            <li><a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/204923/Augmented-Reality-PLUS" target="_blank">Augmented Reality PLUS</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/190687/Espionage-Mission-Generator" target="_blank">Espionage Mission Generator</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/190623/Military-Mission-Generator" target="_blank">Military Mission Generator</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/192001/Area-Building-and-Room-Generator" target="_blank">Area/Building and Room Generator</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/191920/300-Mundane-Items-and-Objects" target="_blank">300 Mundane Items and Objects</a></li>
